    <title>Hexo 使用指南</title>
    <link href="https://dark-night-qwq.github.io/2021/12/16/hello-world/"/>
    <id>https://dark-night-qwq.github.io/2021/12/16/hello-world/</id>
    <published>2021-12-16T13:56:06.099Z</published>
    <updated>2021-12-18T01:51:37.477Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎使用 <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/" >Hexo</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span>！下面的文档可以帮助你快速上手和入门，更多帮助可以在官网上查询！</p>        <h2 id="快速开始"   >          <a href="#快速开始" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#快速开始"></a> 快速开始</h2>              <h3 id="新建文章"   >          <a href="#新建文章" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#新建文章"></a> 新建文章</h3>      <figure class="highlight bash"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new Name</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo n Name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>此时会在：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>/source/_posts</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{/source/\_posts}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.06em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">/source/_posts</span></span></span></span></span> 中生成 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Name.md</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Name.md}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Name.md</span></span></span></span></span> 的文件，使用 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Markdown</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Markdown}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Markdown</span></span></span></span></span> 编辑器（这里我推荐使用 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Typora</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Typora}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Typora</span></span></span></span></span> ，在官网上下载以前的免费版）即可打开。</p><p>可以在文件顶部的代码框中更改标签等等。</p><p>更多请见： <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" >Writing</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p>        <h3 id="本地构建"   >          <a href="#本地构建" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#本地构建"></a> 本地构建</h3>      <figure class="highlight bash"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>这时候输入 <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="http://localhost:4000/" >http://localhost:4000/</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span> 就可以在本地查看了。</p><p>查看完 <code>Ctrl C</code> 就行了。</p><p>更多请见： <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html" >Server</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p>        <h3 id="生成文件"   >          <a href="#生成文件" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#生成文件"></a> 生成文件</h3>      <figure class="highlight bash"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>就是直接构建。</p><p>更多请见： <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" >Generating</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p>        <h3 id="部署到站点"   >          <a href="#部署到站点" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#部署到站点"></a> 部署到站点</h3>      <figure class="highlight bash"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>部署完了打开你的博客地址就可以完成了。</p><p>更多请见： <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html" >Deployment</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p>        <h3 id="使用方式"   >          <a href="#使用方式" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#使用方式"></a> 使用方式</h3>      <p>一般直接调用两件套即可。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>然后博客即可正常使用。</p>        <h2 id="注意"   >          <a href="#注意" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#注意"></a> 注意</h2>      <ul><li>以上的命令都需要在终端（最好有管理员权限）运行，注意前面的 $ 。</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
